Man: “What on earth is this?
Rogers: This is a Geiger counter and is used to detect radioactive minerals, such as uranium.
When you put these headphones on, you can actually hear the effects of atoms released by radioactivity in minerals."
Evans: "I'm sure he's giving a shit right now!"
